        <abstract> 
<p>Extremely glad to hear of the aggregation in <hi rend="italic">Nepenthes</hi> glands. Advises on experimenting with cubes of albumen – gives sizes, also suggests cubes of roast meat. Thanks for analyses of secretion of <hi rend="italic">Nepenthes</hi>.</p>  
<p>Asks for cutting of <hi rend="italic">Acacia farnesiana</hi>.</p>  
<p>Longs to examine a species of <hi rend="italic">Desmodium</hi> with three leaflets. Has asked Frank [Darwin] to look for species of <hi rend="italic">Desmodium</hi> with tendrils.</p> 
        </abstract>
